===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #22] id: assert-base-profile-restrictions
Section 4.2
Base Profile restrictions:
- There SHALL be at most two unique Audio Element OBUs.
- There SHALL be at most one Channel-based Audio Element having num_layers > 1.
- There SHALL be at most one Scene-based Audio Element.
- The sum of channels across all Audio Elements in a Mix Presentation before mixing SHALL NOT exceed 18.

